## Customization

### Colors
Edit `css/styles.css` to change the color scheme:
```css
:root {
    --primary-teal: #4A7C7E;
    --dark-teal: #3A6264;
    --light-teal: #E8F4F5;
    --app-blue: #007AFF;
}
```

### Hero Image Rotation Speed
Edit `js/main.js` to change rotation interval (default: 4000ms):
```javascript
setInterval(() => {
    // Change 4000 to desired milliseconds
}, 4000);
```

### Contact Information
Update contact details in all HTML files:
- Email addresses
- Phone numbers
- Physical address (in Privacy Policy)
- Social media links

